{{新约圣经}}

'''耶稣的比喻'''是《[[新约圣经|新约圣经]]》的《[[四福音书|四福音书]]》（主要在三卷[[对观福音|对观福音]]）中出现的一些[[比喻|比喻]]（包含[[寓言|寓言]]），它们在[[耶稣|耶稣]]的教导中大量出现。

这些比喻大部分都非常朴素、令人难忘，每个比喻都传达某一种特别的教训。例如，耶稣用[[麵酵的比喻|麵酵的比喻]]和[[芥菜种的比喻|芥菜种的比喻]]来形容[[神的国|神的国]]。<!--（an image usually meant as corruption）。Like his aphorisms, Jesus' parables were often surprising and paradoxical。[[好撒马利亚人的比喻|好撒马利亚人的比喻]]，例如, turned expectations on their head with the despised [[撒马利亚人|撒马利亚人]] proving to be the wounded man's neighbor. The parables were simple and memorable enough to survive in an oral tradition before being written down years after Jesus' death. -->
<!-- His parables are sometimes interpreted as allegories in the gospels themselves and in Christian tradition. In such an allegory, each element corresponds metaphorically to a class of people (e.g., false Christians), a heavenly reward, or some other topic. The [[gospel_of_John|gospel of John]] includes allegories but no parables. -->
<!-- 在西方文化中，they are the best known examples of stories referred to as [[比喻|比喻]], and so form [[原型|原型]] for the term ''parable''. -->

==出现==
[[File:Guercino_Return_of_the_prodigal_son.jpg|thumb]]
耶稣的比喻出现在《[[新约圣经|新约圣经]]》的3卷《[[对观福音|对观福音]]》以及[[偽典|偽典]]《[[多马福音|多马福音]]》之中。根据某些解释，《[[约翰福音|约翰福音]]》也包含一个比喻。

根据一项研究<ref>[http://www.bibletexts.com/texts/parables.htm Parables of Jesus in the canonical gospels and the Gospel of Thomas] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bibletexts.com/texts/parables.htm |date=20210420140824 }}, edited by Robert Nguyen Cramer</ref>，[[路加福音|路加福音]]包含的比喻最多（24个），其中独有的比喻数目也最多（10个）。[[马太福音|马太福音]]包含23个比喻，其中独有的有6个。次经[[多马福音|多马福音]]包含15个比喻，其中有2个是独有的。[[马可福音|马可福音]]包含8个比喻，其中独有的有1个（[[种子的比喻|种子的比喻]]）。[[约翰福音|约翰福音]]只包含1个比喻——15章中的[[葡萄树的比喻|葡萄树]]。

这些比喻在正式写成文字以前，已经经由口述的方式流传了许多年。<!-- The hypothetical [[Q_document|Q document]] is seen as a source for parables in Matthew and Luke. -->
<!-- Parables also exist in the [[旧约|旧约]] and in many other writings, see ''[[parable|parable]]''. -->

